  "title": "Infant Educarer",
  "description": "<p>Centre is located at <u>Yishun Industrial Street 1</u> is looking for <strong>Beginning</strong> / <strong>Infant Educarers</strong> who love little babies.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>To create and set up a safe, pleasant, conducive and engaging environment suitable for the care and nurture of infants aged 2 months to 18 months old, and deliver quality care to these precious little ones.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<p>- To deliver developmental-appropriate programme to infants</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To create and set up a conducive environment, including the preparation of age-appropriate teaching-aids</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Part of a team to love and make the babies feel secure as part of providing the children \"a home away from home\".</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Care for the health, hygiene, safety and growth needs of the infants</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Role requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<p>- Minimum Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), Certificate in Infant and Toddler Care and Development with Early Years Development Framework (CITC+EYDF) or its equivalent</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Willingness to work in an infantcare environment with infants</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- Experience is not a must but will be a bonus</p>\n<p>Please <strong>WhatsApp us at 97440878</strong> if you are keen to explore joining us.</p>",
