    "description": "<p>OUR BELIEFS</p>\n<p>We believe children are precious gifts from above to be treasured. The people they meet in their early years have a big impact on their lives and values as they grow.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>VISION</p>\n<p>- To be a fruitful vineyard, where all-rounded and confident learners blossom.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>MISSION</p>\n<p>- To weave fun and beautiful childhood memories through purposeful play and positive relationships</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To seed the love for learning through an engaging quality curriculum</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>- To mould young minds with wholesome values</p>\n<p><br></p>",
